Answer:


Show code
top_by_category &lt;- GLOBAL_TOP_10 |&gt;
  group_by(category, show_title) |&gt;
  summarise(total_hours = sum(weekly_hours_viewed, na.rm = TRUE), .groups = "drop") |&gt;
